1. Moram da pozovem *hitne* službe odmah. (*Hitne* - Nominative singular, "I have to call emergency services right away.")
2. *Hitne* intervencije su spasile život mnogim ljudima. (*Hitne* - Genitive plural, "Emergency interventions have saved many people's lives.")
3. Doktor je rekao da moram da idem u *hitnu* pomoć. (*Hitna* - Accusative singular, "The doctor said I have to go to the emergency room.")
4. Ova situacija zahteva *hitne* mere. (*Hitne* - Accusative plural, "This situation requires urgent measures.")
5. *Hitni* poziv upućen je vatrogascima. (*Hitni* - Nominative singular, "An urgent call was made to the firefighters.")
6. Potrebna nam je *hitna* pomoć! (*Hitna* - Nominative singular, "We need emergency help!")
7. Vozilo *hitne* pomoći stiglo je za samo nekoliko minuta. (*Hitne* - Genitive singular, "The ambulance arrived in just a few minutes.")
8. Molim vas da pozovete *hitnu* ako primetite bilo kakve simptome. (*Hitnu* - Accusative singular, "Please call the emergency services if you notice any symptoms.")
9. Hitne situacije mogu da se dese u bilo kom trenutku. (*Hitne* - Nominative plural, "Emergency situations can happen at any time.")
10. *Hitne* službe su uvek spremne da pomognu. (*Hitne* - Nominative plural, "Emergency services are always ready to help.")